				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Does your girlfriend have a job?  Perhaps your girlfriend's job + her mom's pay could push them over the threshold of being able to afford a low-cost apartment like you were mentioning.  I believe that your g-friend can get emancipated, but I am not sure what the process and/or fees are.
<br />

<br />
